        <prov.body>
          <subprov skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
            <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
              <text>In this Act, <def-term id="DLM351413" xml:lang="en-NZ">specified internal and external complaints mechanisms</def-term> means,â€”</text>
              <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                  <text>for a 2004 Act prisoner, the following mechanisms:</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">i</label>
