                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">4</label>
                  <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                    <text>The Agency may, in either or both of the following circumstances, refuse to amend under <citation jurisdiction="nz">subsection (3)</citation> the maximum grant under <citation jurisdiction="nz">section 20(4)</citation> of legal aid in respect of victims' claims proceedings:</text>
                    <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                      <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                      <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                        <text>the Agency is unable to obtain full information concerning the applicant's financial affairs, because of the default or failure of the applicant:</text>
                      </para>
                    </label-para>
                    <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                      <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                      <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                        <text>if, in the opinion of the Agency, the amount of the contribution that the applicant is likely to be required to make is greater than the likely cost of the proceedings.</text>
                      </para>
                    </label-para>
                  </para>
                </subprov>
              </amend>
            </para>
          </subprov>
        </prov.body>
      </prov>
