idlm:state="UNCHANGED"/><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Legislation_Year" atidlm:value="2005" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Revision_Number" atidlm:value="" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> is amended by inserting, after the expression <quote.in><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 39</citation></quote.in>, the words <amend.in>of this Act, or under <citation jurisdiction="nz">section 20 of the Prisoners' and Victims' Claims Act 2005</citation></amend.in>.</text>
